Falling Blocks Game


* Usage

  ruby falling_blocks.rb [init-level]


* How to Play

  Move left:
    Left (Keyboard)
    Left (Gamepad)

  Move right:
    Right (Keyboard)
    Right (Gamepad)

  Rotate left:
    Z        (Keyboard)
    Button 2 (Gamepad)

  Rotate right:
    X        (Keyboard)
    Button 1 (Gamepad)

  Force to fall:
    Down (Keyboard)
    Down (Gamepad)

  Pause:
    C        (Keyboard)
    Button 3 (GamePad)

  Unpause:
    Any key (Keyboard)
    Any key (Gamepad)


* Score

(base score) * (level)

  base score:
    1 line:   100
    2 lines:  300
    3 lines:  900
    4 lines: 2700
